# Shell directory contract

**Replaces:** `workbench-directory.mdc`, `app-shell-directory.mdc`
**Doctrine:** ADR-0001 (Spatial OS), ADR-0005 (shell unification). If this rule and `AGENTS.md` diverge, follow `AGENTS.md`.

---

## New shell: `components2/app-shell/` (canonical from now on)

`components2/app-shell/` is the **replacement shell** for new route wiring. Import via `#app-shell`.

Shell-level **React providers** live in **`components2/providers/`** (sibling of `app-shell/`, not nested under it). Shell-level **Zustand stores** live in **`components2/stores/`** (same). The `#app-shell` barrel still re-exports `useAppShellStore` for a single public door.

### Public exports

| Symbol | File | Usage |
|---|---|---|
| `AppShell` | `app-shell.tsx` | Org root layout.tsx (RSC entry) |
| `AppShellClient` | `app-shell.client.tsx` | Client chrome ‚Äî mounts AppShellProviders, utility bar |
| `AppSubLayout` | `sub-layout.tsx` | Nested layout.tsx (admin, HRM) ‚Äî in-flow aside |
| `AppSubLayoutClient` | `sub-layout.client.tsx` | Client chrome ‚Äî in-flow aside, local collapse state |
| `AppShellRail` | `nav-rail.client.tsx` | Navigation rail renderer (both modes) |
| `PrimaryNavItem` / `AppShellNavItem` | `nav-item.client.tsx` | Individual nav items (SidebarMenuButton vs standalone) |
| `AppShellSurface` | `surface.tsx` | Page content region (breadcrumbs + body) |
| `AppShellUtilityBar` | `utility-bar.tsx` | L1 top bar (slots only, no business logic) |
| `AppShellRailConfig` | `rail.schema.ts` | Zod schemas + typed rail config |

### `components2/providers/` ‚Äî individual React context providers

| Symbol | File | Purpose |
|---|---|---|
| `AppShellTooltipProvider` | `components2/providers/tooltip-provider.client.tsx` | shadcn Tooltip delay, shell-scoped |
| `AppShellSidebarProvider` | `components2/providers/sidebar-provider.client.tsx` | shadcn SidebarProvider with shell CSS vars + wraps full column |
| `AppShellProviders` | `components2/providers/app-shell-providers.client.tsx` | Composes all providers ‚Äî mount once in `AppShellClient` |

**Key invariant:** `AppShellSidebarProvider` wraps the **entire shell column** including the utility bar header. This is intentional ‚Äî utility-bar components can call `useSidebar()` to control rail collapse without a separate context.

Adding a new provider: create `components2/providers/<concept>-provider.client.tsx`, then compose it inside `app-shell-providers.client.tsx`. One file to change, one place to reason about.

### `components2/stores/` ‚Äî Zustand state (cross-cutting, context-free)

| Symbol | File | State owned |
|---|---|---|
| `useAppShellStore` | `components2/stores/app-shell.store.ts` | `commandOpen`, `notificationCount` |

Zustand stores need no `<Provider>` ‚Äî import `useAppShellStore` in any Client Component inside the shell (prefer `#app-shell` re-export).

Adding new shell state: extend `AppShellStore` in `app-shell.store.ts`. If the store grows beyond ~6 actions, split into a new file under `components2/stores/`.

**Import alias:** `#app-shell` ‚Üí `./components2/app-shell/index.ts` (server-only barrel)
**Import alias:** `#components2/*` ‚Üí `./components2/*` (direct access to components2 primitives)

