## Route layout facade (`AppShell` / `AppSubLayout`)

- **`app/**/layout.tsx`** should import **`AppShell`** and **`AppSubLayout`** from **`#components/workbench`** ‚Äî they are **re-exports** of `WorkbenchShell` / `WorkbenchSubLayout` in [`app-shell.ts`](../../components/workbench/app-shell.ts) with **no wrapper component** (same function reference).
- **Filesystem and implementation** stay under `workbench-*.tsx`; **`WorkbenchShell` / `WorkbenchSubLayout` remain exported** from the workbench barrel for compatibility and tests.

